c: 9
v: 99
t: "Ama Barril madabah tan Qarabak Yallaa kee ellecaboh ayról yaamine maray Yallih gitah yaceeh yanim yallal isi xayyossaah kay kacanu edde geyaah kay farmoytih dooqa edde geyamkeh tet haysita mari keenit yan, Oobbiya!diggah tama taamoomi yallal ken xayyossa, Yalli isi Racmatah isi Jannat ken culse-le, diggah Yalli dambi cabti- li xuwawli kinni"